{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, since deliberation explicitly highlights these conflicts, we are particularly interested in examining its effect on human perceptions of AI and the overall decision-making experience.",
    "Specifically, using our proposed concept of Human-AI Deliberation as a research probe, we aim to explore the following research questions.• RQ1: How will Human-AI Deliberation affect task performance and humans' reliance on AI suggestions?",
    "• RQ2: How will Human-AI Deliberation affect humans' perceptions of the AI partner and their user experience?",
    "• RQ3: How will humans perceive the effectiveness of the proposed Human-AI Deliberation and what can be improved for future Human-AI Deliberation design?To answer these questions, we conducted an exploratory study using a graduate admissions task.",
    "We recruited participants with graduate admissions experience (at least once admitted to a graduate program) on Prolific and asked them to predict an applicant's chance of getting an offer based on the applicant's profile."
  ]
}